				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Gila monsters feed mainly on bird and reptile eggs, but will also eat small birds, small mammals, frogs, lizards, insects and carrion.  Gila monsters have an excellent sense of smell to dig up nests buried underground!
						</text>
