				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Gila monsters have almost no natural predators. Occasionally Gila eggs or young lizards could be preyed upon by coyotes or skunks. The main threat to adult Gila monsters is loss of habitat.
						</text>
