					Livin' Gila Monster Style!
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							The slow moving Gila monster is the only known venomous lizard native to the United States. Even though it is venomous, the Gila monster is so slow it poses very little danger to humans.
						</text>
